column5: awesome job as usual  You certainly have those smallies dialed in.  Tough year for us our smallie count was way down , although so was the number of hours on the water .  Keep it up  TB

Awesome day Steve!  That's bizarre about the Mountain Dew, but then you never know... I remember my grandfather telling me that in the war, in the trenches they'd pee on each others wounds as urine supposedly has antiseptic qualities LOL!
beauty fish dude - especially for a small lake! good work.
